<p>Again, this post is about the design, not the content of the résumé. The idea is that you should adapt the template for your needs.</p>

<p>The example template is for a law student, in which case education is most important.</p>

<p>I find the &#8220;objective&#8221; section a waste of space. No matter how you wordsmith it, isn&#8217;t the objective always to simply get a job?</p>

